            operations effectively.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <!-- Color Styling -->
        <div
          class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"
          data-aos="flip-up"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          data-aos-duration="1200"
        >
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
