          </h2>
          <p
            class="lead text-muted"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-delay="200"
            data-aos-duration="1400"
          >
            Everything you need to launch your HOA website professionally.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1600">
          <div class="d-flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="ri-file-code-line text-primary fs-2"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
