        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="1600">
          <div class="d-flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="ri-css3-line text-primary fs-2"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold">CSS & SCSS</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                Organized SCSS files with variables and mixins for easy customization.
